title: France national football team results (2020–present)
text:
This article provides details of international <a href="Association%20football">football</a> games played by the <a href="France%20national%20football%20team">France national football team</a> from 2020 to present. The team reached the <a href="2021%20UEFA%20Nations%20League%20Finals">UEFA Nations League Finals</a> for the first time. Later, they finished as top of Group F often described as <a href="Group%20of%20death">Group of death</a> in Euro 2020.
